  "instructions": [
    "Heat a molcajete over medium heat.",
    "Add a small amount of oil and swirl to coat.",
    "Add 2-3 pieces of robata-grilled onions and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add 2-3 pieces of sliced jalape\u00166os and cook for another minute.",
    "Add 2-3 beef strips and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, until cooked through.",
    "Add the red Thai curry paste and cook for 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add the natural yoghurt, fish sauce, brown sugar, rice vinegar, chili flakes, toasted peanuts, and toasted coriander seeds. Whisk until well combined.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Warm the tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by placing a few pieces of beef onto a tortilla, followed by a spoonful of the spicy Thai sauce, some shredded cheese, fresh cilantro, and a lime wedge.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Repeat with the remaining ingredients and serve.",
    "Garnish with toasted cumin seeds and serve."
  ],
